Eyes-and-ears Sensor Board: Build Schedule
===

Elements:
- sensors
  - water temperature
  - air temperature and humidity (on board)
  - photo-active radiation (or at least light; on board)
  - water levels (5)
- actuator: 433MHz transmitter

